    • Field Detail

      • priceMap

        private java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.lang.Double>>>> priceMap
        Hash map which keep tracks of the prices. The first key is the format (2D or 3D). The second key is the day (Monday - Friday). The third key is the timing (Before 6 or After 6). The fourth key is the type (Normal, Student, Senior). The value is the price.
